Text.value:
"# Anchors
## Anchors to **relinquish** to this blueprint.

### Anchor A
* Indicates location of relaxed hand
* Move to where wrist will not bend at all

### Anchor B
* Indicates pointer location relative to screen
* Not editable

### Anchor C
* Hand anchor
* Adjust position so the tip of the pen aligns with pointer

### Anchor D
* Arm pole target
* Adjust to where elbow should point to"
